text: Anticrates is a genus of moths of the Lacturidae family. ==Selected species== *Anticrates crocophaea Meyrick, 1921 *Anticrates electropis Meyrick, 1921 *Anticrates metreta (Turner, 1903) *Anticrates paraxantha (Meyrick, 1907) *Anticrates phaedima Turner, 1913 *Anticrates zapyra Meyrick, 1907 ==References== Category:Zygaenoidea Category:Zygaenoidea genera
